{"tid":2196729,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府施壓 逼僱主率員檢測  延長三日谷數 工會斥卑鄙","createTime":"2020-09-10T06:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T06:13:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"129521e80c92a9b97ecc6c9e8a15a82c5171e4a0","tid":2196729,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/IQRMOJSGTFEJ7AGRMZMRAJFW5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FIQRMOJSGTFEJ7AGRMZMRAJFW5Q%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEx4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=eb153e70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FIQRMOJSGTFEJ7AGRMZMRAJFW5Q%2F&h=38910bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/IQRMOJSGTFEJ7AGRMZMRAJFW5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n政府施壓 逼僱主率員檢測 <br />\n延長三日谷數 工會斥卑鄙<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府全民檢測推行九日，市民反應冷淡，只有約142.3萬人參與，佔本港人口不足兩成，政府為求「谷數」，繼教育局去信全港官校促校方呼籲家長參加檢測後，昨日宣佈第二度延長計劃多三日至下周一，企圖增加參與率。食物及衞生局長陳肇始更出口術，「提醒」政府正逐步放寬社交距離措施，呼籲各行業老闆帶同員工進行檢測。有僱主及工會質疑政府逼商界向員工施壓參加檢測，直斥卑鄙。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大龍鳳僅揪出八隱形個案<br />\n<br />\n負責統籌計劃的公務員事務局長聶德權昨於記者會上表示，截至昨日下午2時，已有142.3萬人次接受檢測，考慮到檢測中心運作。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZYi1p8IqE-kLnwMO2hBALs3un4Y=/3322x2215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DTC3ETLXY5GMVGJ7UN264IPEE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZYi1p8IqE-kLnwMO2hBALs3un4Y%3D%2F3322x2215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDTC3ETLXY5GMVGJ7UN264IPEE4.jpg&h=086e1bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港府昨宣佈延長全民檢測計劃多三日至下周一，整個計劃合共14日，但檢測中心將大減至57間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未回應會否強制公務員<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始則表示，由於有兩名參與計劃的外傭確診，她呼籲外傭僱主與外傭積極參與計劃。除向外傭及其僱主「埋手」外，陳肇始更向商界「落藥」，指疫情漸趨穩定，政府正謹慎地逐步放寬處所和行業的社交距離措施，「呼籲呢啲企業，不論是將會放寬、考慮放寬或已放寬，都希望佢哋嘅員工或老闆同員工一齊檢測，從而令員工及市民用這些設施更安心」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：中檢獲欽點 第四間國企參與化驗<br />\n<br />\n被追問政府未來數日會否為「追數」而強制公務員參與檢測，聶德權強調，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席吳敏兒指出，陳肇始相關說法涉威迫逼誘商界向員工施壓參加全。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CBD7IluqbQH2ugR94dawqlVtUmw=/1357x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VO5ELNGZPNBLTLNKS7FRQ64RLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCBD7IluqbQH2ugR94dawqlVtUmw%3D%2F1357x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVO5ELNGZPNBLTLNKS7FRQ64RLA.jpg&h=10c6991e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林鄭聲稱代表香港市民，向內地支援隊致謝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bt_9__Ku22ruDNvmlL3OEak_pm8=/1021x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WCR2Q2DZDRB75NWB36DB6WJOQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBt_9__Ku22ruDNvmlL3OEak_pm8%3D%2F1021x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWCR2Q2DZDRB75NWB36DB6WJOQU.jpg&h=28fc4a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聶德權昨在記者會上仍無公開整個全民檢測的開支。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員：交唔到數急就章<br />\n<br />\n香港中小企食店聯盟召集人林瑞華亦質疑政府為谷數而出口術，指第三波疫情爆發是林鄭政府防<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林鄭昨晚聯同多名官員到訪氣膜實驗室，稱聲代表香港市民，向工作人員「特別是內地核酸檢。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ip-H_crZAWqwgM0SoqCzCzAam3c=/780x756/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TC57BLH3KJBNHBOR4BUUT37ZLY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fip-H_crZAWqwgM0SoqCzCzAam3c%3D%2F780x756%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTC57BLH3KJBNHBOR4BUUT37ZLY.gif&h=e8b0d016&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}